{ //Dwarf

  //Dwarf Gift Tastes
  "CDE_Dwarf_GoldPumpkin": "I have no idea what this is. But I love it.#$e#No, you may not have it back.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_RockCandy": "You are truly offering me this?#$b#...Give me. Give me. I bid you endless prosperity.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Pearl": "A stone... from the bottom of the sea? How enchanting.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_PrismaticShard": "You have undeniably achieved the highest skill as a miner. I hereby accept you as one of my own.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_RabbitsFoot": "What a strange object. And yet, you say it is imbued with good luck?#$b#I will cherish it. Good luck is what I need most of all right now.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Emerald": "My hands work faster with an emerald nearby. I thank you humbly.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Ruby": "Many thanks. This stone houses a powerful battle fury. Did you know that?",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Amethyst": "Thank you. I can use this to knock away the shadow brutes if they get too close.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Topaz": "A protective stone? Why yes, it's exactly what I need. I give you my humblest thanks.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_Jade": "Thank you. The power of jade is fickle, but when activated, it may be the greatest power of all.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_OmniGeode": "For me? Why thank you. *shake shake*#$b#I can tell... there's a prismatic shard inside!#$e#...Just kidding.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_LavaEel": "Oh! It's fresh! It's wriggling! And you're giving it to me?#$b#*slurrrrrrrrrrp* *smack*#$e#...#$b#Got any more?",
  "CDE_Dwarf_LemonStone": "Ahh, I'll grind this up with a little limestone and I'll have a delicious treat.#$e#No, you humans should not eat ground-up stones. I hear it will wreck your innards.#$b#Didn't you know that?",

  //Dwarf's Misc Dialogue
  //these lines target files other than the standard characters/dialogue/Dwarf location such as unmarried rainy dialogue
  "CDE_Dwarf_rainy_1": "Rain... It's almost mythical to us. Some of us dwarves live our entire lives without ever experiencing it.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_rainy_2": "Humans seem to complain about rain, yet you choose to live on the surface. Why is that?",
  "CDE_Dwarf_rainy_3": "Delving deep today, are we?#$e#The monsters are appearing in great numbers. Be careful.",

  //Dwarf's Standard Dialogue

  //Special Dialogue
  "CDE_Dwarf_repeated_1": "A few times, I have seen a strange, blue human climbing down through the mines.#$e#At least, I think he's one of you humans.#$e#I don't trust him.",
  "CDE_Dwarf_repeated_2": "I'm impressed by how much your species has advanced in the past 100 years alone.#$b#Are humans always in a rush like that?",
  "CDE_Dwarf_repeated_3": "The old way of my life is gone. I must connect with humans, but I also do not think your species would receive me well if I walked through the town.#$e#The light outside would drive me crazy in a matter of minutes, too.",
