  "CDE_Dwarf_Sun": "Care to buy anything today?",
  "CDE_Dwarf_winterSun": "Ah, yes. It's true that there's a shrine of death near here. Some humans must have tunneled straight into it some time ago.#$e#I can't say exactly where it came from. Certainly not my people. And the shadow people have also denied it.#$e#Have you been there?",
